  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Wave Equation
Formula: v = fλ
Note:    Speed of wave = frequency × wavelength

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Boyle's Law
Formula: P₁V₁ = P₂V₂
Note:    Pressure and volume inversely proportional at constant T

Domain:  Medicine
Topic:   Germ Theory
Formula: Microorganisms cause disease
Note:    Pasteur/Koch; foundation of modern medicine

Domain:  Geology
Topic:   Age of Earth
Formula: 4.54 billion years
Note:    Determined by radiometric dating of oldest rocks/meteorites

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   ATP
Formula: ADP + Pi → ATP
